text: Ivan Litvinovich (born 26 June 2001) is a Belarusian trampoline gymnast. In 2019, he won the silver medal in the men's individual event at the 2019 Trampoline World Championships held in Tokyo, Japan. In 2018, he competed in the boys' trampoline and mixed multi-discipline team events at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics in Buenos, Argentina without winning a medal.
